                        "name": "Player Core pg. 458",
                        "type": "link"
                      },
                      "name": "Player Core",
                      "page": 458,
                      "type": "source"
                    }
                  ],
                  "text": "A mental effect can alter the target\u2019s mind. It has no effect on an object or a mindless creature.",
